{"tid":1658893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國開騷籲海外港人撐抗爭運動 何韻詩哽咽高唱：生於亂世有種責任","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T17:26:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84c3c9da04ee25c6a198541d8a01ac9e934fe0a8","tid":1658893,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191016/20787550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F20787550&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=ef924a91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F20787550&h=79168d18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191016/20787550</a><br />\n<br />\n美國開騷籲海外港人撐抗爭運動<br />\n何韻詩哽咽高唱：生於亂世有種責任<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191016/large/1571145510_9302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571145510_9302.jpg&h=78b941ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩前日在紐約開騷，唱《艷光四射》時數度哽咽。 記者胡凱文紐約傳真<br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果》紐約直擊】何韻詩前日在美國紐約曼哈頓Town Hall舉行演唱會，開場前，已有人在場外高呼「香港人，反抗」及「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號。何韻詩先唱《如無意外》、《天使藍》等熱門歌曲打頭陣，然後以許冠傑的《同舟共濟》來表達對香港這個家的感情，及後當她唱到《艷光四射》的歌詞「生於亂世有種責任」時，她更忍不住哽咽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191016/large/1571145509_cbbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571145509_cbbc.jpg&h=6bcc584e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿詩除了獻唱自己歌曲，亦唱出多首與香港逆權運動有關的歌曲，包括《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191016/large/1571145509_a2e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571145509_a2e9.jpg&h=2a33e500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩在紐約曼哈頓Town Hall開騷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191016/large/1571145509_1dca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571145509_1dca.jpg&h=135e5fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全場觀眾起立一起大合唱，場面感動。<br />\n<br />\n「光明時間終會來臨」<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩在台上呼籲海外港人支持香港的抗爭運動，她說：「我對人民嘅聲音仍然充滿信心，音樂其實不應該只係娛樂大家，係應該去將人民嘅聲音、人民經歷嘅事紀錄下來。我哋年輕嘅新一代，有好多好有才華嘅人，奈何我哋𠵱家要睇住佢哋，去面對困難。但唔緊要，我深信光明嘅時間終會來臨。究竟乜嘢時候，其實冇人會知道，但我哋要做足心理準備，佢隨時都可以嚟到。」然後阿詩唱出《Do You Hear The People Sing》，並與台灣的鋼琴家獻唱了《願榮光歸香港》，在場觀眾都站立一起大合唱。最後在安歌位時，何韻詩唱出《肥媽有話兒》，台下觀眾紛紛大叫，大家的情緒十分高漲，最後，她在全場手機燈光下，唱了一首《木紋》作結。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰：佢付出好多<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志常委羅冠聰亦有到場欣賞，他指何韻詩作出不少犧牲：「最感動係佢提到自己作為一個歌手，同佢𠵱家身份嘅掙扎。其實明白佢付出咗好多，為咗香港，佢放棄如日方中嘅事業，一個佢好喜歡做嘅角色，而選擇咗同香港人一齊走，所以佢好值得大家尊重同敬佩。」 <br />\n<br />\n駐紐約記者胡凱文報道 <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n董敏莉拍咀戲老公笑笑口"},{"pid":"03a8751ac4ffd64568d469aeb605b21174ab9214","tid":1658893,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3cdb331d1e30945533a6ccc7f683a581a05b8e58","tid":1658893,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"雖然我都屌佢左膠思想，但無可否認佢嘅付出犧牲係大，值得尊敬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c8d9a7c226a25f40b020d546f4cee107322b4d","tid":1658893,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><sp