aces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f0c954982937a92e58d2ec384322fea479c08a","tid":1658893,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6e49179472f0db85d9bb1ccb3fe6c319d0543ff8","tid":1658893,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e35684cb239eaf1f721dfc28d5f3a00a55c1e6","tid":1658893,"uid":278712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有一種level 99的職業：叫何韻詩"}]}